{"tid":432562,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(新手求問)Nexus 5X 死機點搞","createTime":"2017-10-11T15:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T17:33:19.000Z","uid":114292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b235c4c2c32c64e36fa8ae0d89c408e9f673a91","tid":432562,"uid":114292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩上上下連登個畫面突然卡死左<br />\n無耐就黑左mon<br />\n正常開機開唔到 叉電都無嘢睇<br />\n屋企人話應該係壞底板 所以乜都無反應<br />\n然後我上網見到Power+Volume Down個個fastboot mode<br />\n話如果開唔到依個mode就真係收皮<br />\n個篇文係好簡單話開完揀Recovery Mode就無事<br />\n問題係我揀完-&gt;彈Google字-&gt;又黑mon <br />\n我想知部機壞啲咩 係咪無得救？<br />\n利申 對手機唔多認識 有錯細力屌<br />\n有問題可以再補充"},{"pid":"f66cbb40144f8e2d55b0d54448ae81c3abde810b","tid":432562,"uid":70252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"詳情請參考5x苦主post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5169aabc55edb64a8c0baa22b57acda9ecfe03d9","tid":432562,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"我部機都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾桶見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a872595f411b2f0b80ff9171da07383a7322c677","tid":432562,"uid":114292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"仲有就係我好難先入到一次fastboot mode 唔係下下都得<br />\n有時要長按power+volume down勁耐先有 <br />\n係咪可以打定輸數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e084ba694a8f88528f67672935ec6aeaadf2e24b","tid":432562,"uid":114292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>詳情請參考5x苦主post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪更新個次？有無link<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該巴打先"},{"pid":"b798c42981d9d1612627afa7076bcf7c053b5200","tid":432562,"uid":114292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:39:56.000Z","msg"