\n不過依幾個鐘我成功開到fast boot應該得5-6次 所以我諗都凍過水.."},{"pid":"e7257ae35b264247f04ad74e78b56bb21e724ae3","tid":432562,"uid":125380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:14:15.000Z","msg":"我用緊 想知有咩預防既方法"},{"pid":"4355a0d70ddb295e67a07f053ada8c6dfcb89492","tid":432562,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"其實我已經開過post, 你地自己入去慢慢睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Nexus 5X 6P Bootloop問題</strong></span></span> <br />\n- 如經Google Play購買，可自己聯絡Google 申請退款或換機 (已過保養期亦可)<br />\n- 有消息指，香港Google已更改政策，所有有問題手機交由LG 或 華為負責<br />\n- 如經門市購買，請自行聯絡LG 或 華為代理<br />\n- 經門市購買而又已過保養期，可自行找第三方維修中心重焊或更換CPU<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">詳情參閱：</span></strong><br />\nLG Nexus 5X Bootloop 苦主請入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/159418/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/159418/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n- XDA 已有臨時的解決方法, 使受Bootloop影響的手機成功進入系統, 大家可以用此方法為手機進行備份 (只限已Unlock Booltloader 手機)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意: 此方法並不能永久修復有關問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/nexus-5x-bootloop-fix-boot-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xda-developers.com%2Fnexus-5x-bootloop-fix-boot-phone%2F&d=yPJiFznuub29aD1mpa7tkzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bf4b1a06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xda-developers.com/nexus-5x-bootloop-fix-boot-phone/</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/nexus-6p-bootloop-fix/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xda-developers.com%2Fnexus-6p-bootloop-fix%2F&d=yPJiFznuub29aD1mpa7tkzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c61c8c84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xda-developers.com/nexus-6p-bootloop-fix/</a>"},{"pid":"780cc1735cc5a68580672c921e8f64c99c333bc3","tid":432562,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同你一樣情況 係壞底板<br />\n利申 已經壞第二次 正式放棄5x</blockquote><br />\n但開到fast boot 都係壞底板?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我就係想知係咪真係底板<br />\n不過依幾個鐘我成功開到fast boot應該得5-6次 所以我諗都凍過水..</blockquote><br />\n你想試係咪n5x bootloop個通病， 用風筒吹到部機勁熱， 然後成功開機，就一定係底板問題，拎上華強北重焊粒cpu就okay"}]}